Release Notes
New Update:
🔔 How to Set Up Alerts in TradingView
1. Click "Alerts" in TradingView.
2. Click "+ Create Alert".
3. In the "Condition" dropdown, select this script.
4. Choose "Any alert function call".
5. Set Alert Actions (popup, email, notification, etc.).
6. Click "Create" to activate the alerts.
________________________________________
🔹 What This Update Adds
✅ Alerts when Buy & Sell signals appear.
✅ User-friendly alert messages with clear trade signals.
✅ No repainting alerts (alerts trigger only when bar closes).
